    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018362_5_3527-3578",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3527-3578",
      "markText": "如果把认识过程的某一片断（感觉、表象或概念等等）加以夸大、绝对化，使它脱离物质现实，就会导致唯心主义。",
      "totalCount": 900,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018362&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3527&rangeEnd=3578",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0aa32f40813ab6dacg012267?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3527&rangeEnd=3578"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018362_5_14075-14109",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "14075-14109",
      "markText": "马克思说：“哲学家们只是用不同的方式解释世界，而问题在于改变世界。”",
      "totalCount": 756,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018362&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=14075&rangeEnd=14109",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0aa32f40813ab6dacg012267?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=14075&rangeEnd=14109"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018362_2_19446-19516",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "19446-19516",
      "markText": "是什么力量使得动物的脑过渡到人脑、动物心理过渡到人的意识呢？辩证唯物主义回答说，是劳动。劳动是猿变成人的决定因素，是人的意识产生的决定因素。",
      "totalCount": 736,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018362&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=19446&rangeEnd=19516",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0aa32f40813ab6dacg012267?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=19446&rangeEnd=19516"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018362_2_1354-1401",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "1354-1401",
      "markText": "任何一种物质形态都是从另一种物质形态转化来的，物质是永恒存在的，物质不能被创造，也不能被消灭。",
      "totalCount": 732,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018362&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=1354&rangeEnd=1401",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0aa32f40813ab6dacg012267?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=1354&rangeEnd=1401"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018362_5_2373-2437",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2373-2437",
      "markText": "唯心主义作为一种哲学体系，作为一种完整的世界观，是在阶级社会中形成的，其社会根源就是阶级剥削制度本身和体力劳动与脑力劳动的分离。",
      "totalCount": 697,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018362&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2373&rangeEnd=2437",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0aa32f40813ab6dacg012267?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2373&rangeEnd=2437"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018362_5_2640-2675",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2640-2675",
      "markText": "在阶级社会里，体力劳动和脑力劳动的分离，是唯心主义哲学产生的必要条件。",
      "totalCount": 689,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018362&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2640&rangeEnd=2675",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0aa32f40813ab6dacg012267?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2640&rangeEnd=2675"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018362_2_452-484",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "452-484",
      "markText": "世界是物质的世界，物质世界永远按照自己固有的规律运动着、发展着。",
      "totalCount": 672,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018362&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=452&rangeEnd=484",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0aa32f40813ab6dacg012267?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=452&rangeEnd=484"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018362_5_2805-2869",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2805-2869",
      "markText": "历史上的某些剥削阶级或其中的某些集团，当他们还能代表一定的历史进步的倾向而和反动没落阶级作斗争时，也可能支持和提倡唯物主义哲学。",
      "totalCount": 663,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018362&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2805&rangeEnd=2869",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0aa32f40813ab6dacg012267?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2805&rangeEnd=2869"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018362_5_3959-3997",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3959-3997",
      "markText": "辩证法认为，世界上一切事物都是发展变化的，事物发展的原因在于它内部的矛盾性。",
      "totalCount": 648,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018362&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3959&rangeEnd=3997",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0aa32f40813ab6dacg012267?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3959&rangeEnd=3997"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018362_5_1025-1071",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1025-1071",
      "markText": "哲学就是关于世界观的学问，哲学观点就是人们对于世界上的一切事物、对于整个世界的最根本的观点。",
      "totalCount": 624,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018362&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1025&rangeEnd=1071",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0aa32f40813ab6dacg012267?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1025&rangeEnd=1071"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018362_2_15581-15671",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "15581-15671",
      "markText": "事物发展的规律不依人的意志为转移，但人们在客观规律面前并不是无能为力的。人们能够认识客观规律，并利用这种认识来指导自己的行动，以达到改造自然，改造社会，为人民群众谋福利的伟大目的。",
      "totalCount": 595,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018362&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=15581&rangeEnd=15671",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0aa32f40813ab6dacg012267?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=15581&rangeEnd=15671"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018362_2_53759-53833",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "53759-53833",
      "markText": "真正的革命者，不仅要有勇于进行根本变革的革命精神，而且在根本变革的条件还没有完全具备时，要耐心细致地进行量的准备工作。这样，才能真正促进事物的发展。",
      "totalCount": 595,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018362&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=53759&rangeEnd=53833",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0aa32f40813ab6dacg012267?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=53759&rangeEnd=53833"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018362_5_2508-2549",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2508-2549",
      "markText": "统治阶级的思想代表，由于日益远离生产实践活动，总是夸大精神活动的作用，把它绝对化。",
      "totalCount": 558,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018362&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2508&rangeEnd=2549",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0aa32f40813ab6dacg012267?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2508&rangeEnd=2549"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018362_5_441-460",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "441-460",
      "markText": "马克思主义是革命的工人阶级的思想武器。",
      "totalCount": 540,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018362&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=441&rangeEnd=460",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0aa32f40813ab6dacg012267?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=441&rangeEnd=460"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018362_2_37867-37899",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "37867-37899",
      "markText": "普遍性存在于特殊性之中，共性存在于个性之中，绝对存在于相对之中。",
      "totalCount": 504,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018362&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=37867&rangeEnd=37899",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0aa32f40813ab6dacg012267?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=37867&rangeEnd=37899"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018362_2_29572-29667",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "29572-29667",
      "markText": "因此，想问题、做事情都要充分估计到条件的作用，要具体地分析客观条件和主观条件、有利条件和不利条件。离开条件去想问题，其结果只会成为没有根据的空想；不顾条件去做事情，就会成为乱撞乱碰的鲁莽家。",
      "totalCount": 496,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018362&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=29572&rangeEnd=29667",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0aa32f40813ab6dacg012267?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=29572&rangeEnd=29667"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018362_5_2152-2224",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2152-2224",
      "markText": "哲学史上的二元论，企图把物质和精神看做两种各自独立、互相平行的世界本质。它摇摆在唯物主义和唯心主义之间，因此在实际上并不是真正独立的第三种派别。",
      "totalCount": 486,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018362&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2152&rangeEnd=2224",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0aa32f40813ab6dacg012267?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2152&rangeEnd=2224"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018362_5_17038-17135",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "17038-17135",
      "markText": "我们学习马克思主义哲学的目的，是为了和资产阶级的世界观以及一切错误思想进行斗争，改造自己的主观世界，树立革命的、科学的世界观，并以它为指导来观察和处理一切问题，更好地推进社会主义和共产主义事业。",
      "totalCount": 462,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018362&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=17038&rangeEnd=17135",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0aa32f40813ab6dacg012267?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=17038&rangeEnd=17135"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018362_2_44591-44642",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "44591-44642",
      "markText": "任何矛盾双方都是不断斗争的，斗争的结果，最终必然导致矛盾双方的转化、矛盾的解决，而不是矛盾双方的调和。",
      "totalCount": 450,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018362&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=44591&rangeEnd=44642",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0aa32f40813ab6dacg012267?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=44591&rangeEnd=44642"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018362_5_4458-4497",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4458-4497",
      "markText": "只有马克思主义的辩证唯物主义的哲学，才能包含最彻底的唯物主义和最彻底的辩证法。",
      "totalCount": 448,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018362&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4458&rangeEnd=4497",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0aa32f40813ab6dacg012267?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4458&rangeEnd=4497"
